subsection_name: mun-trung-ca-o-lung.json_3_Symptoms of acne on the back?
subsection_content: A common symptom of back acne is acne along the shoulders and upper back. Over time, acne can "spread" downward and develop to the waist area. Pimples can grow individually or in clusters and cause pain. In some cases, multiple types of acne may appear at the same time.

mun trung ca o lung.json. Symptoms of acne on the back?
A common symptom of back acne is acne along the shoulders and upper back. Over time, acne can "spread" downward and develop to the waist area. Pimples can grow individually or in clusters and cause pain. In some cases, multiple types of acne may appear at the same time.
